Class PlasticButtonUI

java.lang.Object
  javax.swing.plaf.ComponentUI

              javax.swing.plaf.metal.MetalButtonUI
                  com.jgoodies.plaf.plastic.PlasticButtonUI
public class PlasticButtonUI
extends javax.swing.plaf.metal.MetalButtonUI

The JGoodies Plastic L&F implementation of ButtonUI.

It differs from the superclass MetalButtonUI in that it can add a pseudo 3D effect, and that it listens to the jgoodies.isNarrow property to choose an appropriate margin.

Author:
Karsten Lentzsch
